snippet: Wreckage believed to be of the cargo ship El Faro, which was lost off the Bahamas during Hurricane Joaquin, was discovered, American officials said.
abstract: American search team reports finding wreckage believed to be that of cargo ship El Faro; vessel disappeared in October off Bahamas, along with 33 crew members, during Hurricane Joaquin.
lead_paragraph: Wreckage believed to be of the cargo ship El Faro, which was lost off the Bahamas during Hurricane Joaquin, was discovered, American officials said.

headline.main: Wreckage of Lost U.S. Ship Believed Found
headline.print_headline: Wreckage of Lost U.S. Ship Believed Found
